{"tid":1924274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國論壇文宣/鍵戰請入] 跪求預防武漢肺炎嘅英文素材","createTime":"2020-03-13T15:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T15:48:58.000Z","uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c366340f3422a2af4656b8803fd9b1b2a5118e3e","tid":1924274,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:00:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟一向有上一個外國嘅體育論壇<br />\n<br />\n論壇上嘅外國人呢排都好緊張武漢肺炎，咁小弟當然大蛇隨棍上 share 相關文宣大大力屌共產黨啦<br />\n<br />\n但屌得太多，有外國網友睇唔順眼，話我淨係識屌共產黨，無提供&quot;有用信息&quot; (其實我有 share 到18種語言嘅預防肺炎片，無咩人理)<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴絲，除左果條18種語言嘅片之外，仲有無其他英文素材可以參考？<br />\n<br />\n非常感謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1279907de4a596faadfe1537e5b3c07d55afd8f7","tid":1924274,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d86b67756048d35bc04865f980acf83ff079791","tid":1924274,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a66d3c2bb17aa4324546a8b3886d59bc847c9a42","tid":1924274,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37fc6934cff4fd5ea3a3f5ad4659024ef29bb6bc","tid":1924274,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:03:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be632060cdbbd80dbbeabaaae7ad47c09de1d7fe","tid":1924274,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:03:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a8f096ea72b1228b9c79ed0634330643f1491a5","tid":1924274,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c01e371f6dd1e53ec86139e2d6da6e082703db8","tid":1924274,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:03:42.000Z"